1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:12,530
♪Longing during the day
and loneliness at night♪

2
00:00:12,830 --> 00:00:19,700
♪Clouds drift and curl,
and the cold rain falls again♪

3
00:00:20,460 --> 00:00:26,100
♪Green grass once dreamed of the world
and enlightened me♪

4
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:32,990
♪I crossed the sea of suffering
but couldn't escape your gaze♪

5
00:00:33,190 --> 00:00:39,930
♪Look at the bright moon
across the Milky Way♪

6
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:46,990
♪All love poems will record our story
from now on♪

7
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:53,700
♪The thought of the distant mountain
makes my heart ache for my hometown♪

8
00:00:53,840 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Stone of Three Lifetimes reflects fate.
You once rode past on horseback♪

9
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,720
=Just Wanna Be With You=

10
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,360
(Adapted From
Zhihu Novelist, Little Qi's)

11
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,260
("Three Marriages
to the Underworld Lord")

12
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:10,260
=Episode 20=

13
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:12,799
Yu.

14
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,680
Where exactly are you taking me?

15
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:15,560
Take a guess.

16
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:16,840
You said it yourself.

17
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,000
You'd do anything with me.

18
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,400
No peeking.

19
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:23,480
So this is the place
you wanted to visit most.

20
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,640
Why are you doing this?

21
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,079
I told you not to peek.

22
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:29,239
This is no fun.

23
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,879
Just so you know, I didn't peek.

24
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,239
It's only because

25
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,719
this is the path us foxfolk use
to go to Cangyun.

26
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,680
I used to wander here all the time.

27
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:43,959
I wanted to see you but couldn't.

28
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:48,159
Over time, I became familiar
with every blade of grass

29
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,159
and tree

30
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,519
as well as the air here.

31
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,359
I've wanted to ask you.

32
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,040
Why did you want to come here?

33
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,359
Because

34
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,359
this place holds our memories.

35
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:04,799
Do you remember it?

36
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,360
Of course.

37
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,879
Wherever you are

38
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,680
is my fondest memory.

39
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,280
Look, it's fireflies!

40
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,439
I'll catch a few for you.

41
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,000
You're the Demon Lord now.

42
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,240
How can you catch fireflies?

43
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,479
So what if I am?

44
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,960
As long as you like them,
I'll catch them for you forever.

45
00:02:47,258 --> 00:02:52,400
♪The wind in the courtyard
has put off the candlelight♪

46
00:02:54,763 --> 00:03:00,887
♪Stars and moonlight
shine through the west window♪

47
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:02,800
(Huai.)

48
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,800
(The future is uncertain.)

49
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:07,080
(If I die because of Aohen,)

50
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,520
(don't grieve for me.)

51
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,879
(You must stay as happy as you are now.)

52
00:03:12,727 --> 00:03:16,130
♪To speak of sorrow♪

53
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:17,800
Look at this.

54
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,080
How beautiful!

55
00:03:24,916 --> 00:03:30,909
♪Tears flow endlessly♪

56
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,680
Yes, how beautiful.

57
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:40,036
♪Appreciate the beauty
that rivals a kingdom's glory♪

58
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:45,400
(If you are as sincere as me,)

59
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:49,000
(then I won't let our love be in vain.)

60
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:04,919
Yu.

61
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,599
I want to marry you properly

62
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,680
and announce it to all three realms.

63
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,039
Sure.

64
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:23,480
(Today, Yu and I are getting married.)

65
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:26,399
(Jiang Zhiyu is now
the Demon Region's new mistress.)

66
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:29,040
(All demons shall follow her lead)

67
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,959
(and protect her for eternity.)

68
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:57,399
Let me remind you.

69
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:01,040
I'm now your wife.

70
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,160
You have to discuss everything with me.

71
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,800
You're already bossing me around, huh?

72
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,279
You said you'd do as I say.

73
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:10,800
My dear.

74
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:14,000
Then today, do I make the call
here in the Demon Region?

75
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,199
Of course.

76
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:23,199
If so, call me Demon Lady.

77
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,399
Yes, my Demon Lady.

78
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,552
Congratulations to the Demon Lady

79
00:05:36,553 --> 00:05:38,120
on the wedding.

80
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:40,939
Congratulations to the Demon Lady

81
00:05:40,940 --> 00:05:42,439
on the wedding.

82
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,120
Congratulations to the Demon Lady

83
00:05:45,121 --> 00:05:46,720
on the wedding.

84
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,967
♪My gaze to you♪

85
00:05:52,196 --> 00:05:55,949
♪Right now I can't hide
the joy in my heart♪

86
00:05:56,014 --> 00:06:01,098
♪It spreads through the swirling mist♪

87
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:05,956
♪You'll never know,
I've never longed for anyone so♪

88
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:06,639
Huai.

89
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:07,639
It's Luo Ying!

90
00:06:12,690 --> 00:06:18,210
♪When our eyes meet,
time itself seems to stand still♪

91
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:22,420
♪I couldn't help
but take one step closer to you♪

92
00:06:22,930 --> 00:06:25,510
♪I'm the fog born in the forest♪

93
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:28,150
♪You're the wind that rises at dusk♪

94
00:06:28,150 --> 00:06:33,240
♪You have traveled a thousand miles.
Deep love and everything♪

95
00:06:33,389 --> 00:06:35,940
♪Even if it's just a moment's pause♪

96
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:43,000
♪How could I be content
with just one look at you?♪

97
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:46,260
♪I'm the fog born in the forest♪

98
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:48,710
♪You're the wind that rises at dusk♪

99
00:06:48,945 --> 00:06:53,670
♪Wherever you go,
my heart quietly follows♪

100
00:06:54,072 --> 00:06:56,870
♪I'll follow you to the ends
of the mountains and forests♪

101
00:06:56,967 --> 00:07:03,620
♪A life adrift at last
finds a place to belong♪

102
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,240
Do you like staring at me so much?

103
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,680
I just can't get enough of you.

104
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,839
Let me help you.

105
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:55,639
Yu.

106
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,279
We've married three times.

107
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,199
Have you ever regretted it?

108
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,240
Not at all.

109
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,000
If there's another life,

110
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:06,680
I'd marry you again.

111
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:28,900
♪Dark clouds cover the stars
without a trace of light♪

112
00:08:30,410 --> 00:08:34,890
♪Waiting for the wind
to clear the grey away♪

113
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:40,720
♪Sudden rain falls
and I get soaked alone♪

114
00:08:40,810 --> 00:08:44,520
♪Even larks know where they belong♪

115
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:50,340
♪It is not about running away♪

116
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:58,540
♪I search for you across the vast sky,
but where are you now?♪

117
00:08:59,410 --> 00:09:04,490
♪I become a wisp of wind,
wiping away the clouds' traces♪

118
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:09,780
♪I long to disappear without a trace,
wrapped in mystery♪

119
00:09:09,890 --> 00:09:13,560
♪If I send your loneliness
back to the sky♪

120
00:09:13,950 --> 00:09:19,310
♪It can only rest inside your dreams♪

121
00:09:19,430 --> 00:09:24,410
♪You and I gaze
at the endless Milky Way♪

122
00:09:24,410 --> 00:09:26,540
♪Holding each other so near♪

123
00:09:26,770 --> 00:09:33,920
♪If I were granted
a pair of splendid wings♪

124
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:38,990
♪I could chase memories
in place of the right to love♪

125
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:41,640
♪But the Milky Way never ends♪

126
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:48,440
♪In this thin robe,
I wait for your reply♪
